A simple multicast ping program taken from chapter 7 in the book
Multicast Sockets.

Remember to set the multicast route for your system to the correct
interface.  My system has eth0 as default gateway, but I want my
multicast to egress eth1:

	route add -net 224.0.0.0/4 dev eth1

Multicast Sockets -- Practical Guide for Programmers
Chapter 7: Multicast Reachability and Scalability
By: 	David Makofske and Kevin Almeroth
ISBN:	1-55860-846-X

